reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on August 26, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great water bottle
reviews.reviewText: For the price this is a great water bottle, love that it comes with extra lids. It holds a lot of water for my 11yr old son. Keeps his water cold all day at school. Only had it for a month so hoping the lid will hold up the entire school year as he is pretty rough with his water bottle.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 10, 2023
reviews.reviewText: Keep ice cold for more than 24 hours easily

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 16, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great Water Bottle
reviews.reviewText: I have bought bottles from Yeti, Hydroflask, and IronFlask. This bottle is just as good and was a great deal less expensive. The extra lids fit on most bottles of equal oz (even my plastic Camelback bottles) so I like having them even though I only use the straw lid for this. Buy it you will love it!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 17, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Exellent, does everything well but doesn't fit in a car cup holder
reviews.reviewText: It's a great insulated container. Keeps cold and hot for hours. Only problem, it doesn't fit in car cup holder.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 3, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Same as Simple Modern
reviews.reviewText: Exact same measurements and lid fit as Simple Modern brand. Quality seems the same as well.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on July 7, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars I like it
reviews.reviewText: I like it well enough, I needed to replace my old bottle. It doesn't keep the water as cold for long.It did have multiple lids just wish you could pick I'll never use the straw top. It is a convenient size and color is pleasant

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 8, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great for staying hydrated
reviews.reviewText: I use this bottle on offshore oil rigs to stay hydrated. It keeps my ice and water cold for a long time . It’s attractive. It came with different lids and an extra straw with a straw cleaning brush. Would buy again.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 5, 2023
reviews.reviewText: Seems like a decent water bottle. However the spout lid was damaged. One side of the spout was sharp. It also does not have an air hole.
